Package uk.gov.gchq.koryphe.tuple

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Tuple<R>
    A Tuple provides a map-like interface to any data structure.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArrayTuple
    An ArrayTuple is a simple implementation of the Tuple interface, backed by an array of Objects, referenced by their index.
    MapTuple<R>
    A MapTuple is an implementation of Tuple backed by a Map.
    ReferenceArrayTuple<R>  
    ReflectiveTuple
    A ReflectiveTuple is a Tuple that wraps an object and treats it as a Tuple by using reflection to call fields directly or via getters.
    ReflectiveTuple.Cache<T extends AccessibleObject>  
    TupleInputAdapter<R,FI>  
    TupleOutputAdapter<R,FO>
